      *    ณ    program.                                               ณ
      *    ณ    PERFORM HEADING-AND-CLEAR-SCREEN.                      ณ
      *    ณ                                                           ณ
      *    ณ To change the screen heading:                             ณ
      *    ณ    MOVE "The new heading" TO CRT-HEADING.                 ณ
      *    ณ    PERFORM CHANGE-HEADING.                                ณ
      *    ณ                                                           ณ
      *    ณ To change the time on the screen:                         ณ
